  "title": "Accounts Executive (Full Sets)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Able to handle full set of accounts</li><li>Responsible for maintaining accurate costing processes for production, and materials.</li><li>Responsible for accurate and timely month-end closing</li><li>Assist in staff payroll matters</li><li>May handle Singapore and/or Malaysia subsidiaries accounting work (if assigned to do so) </li><li>Any other duties as and when assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in Accounting / LCCI or equivalent</li><li>At least 3 years of relevant experience in manufacturing industry</li><li>Meticulous and organized</li><li>Bilingual in English and Mandarin (to liaise with English and Mandarin speaking associates and staff for work)</li><li>Proficient in MS Office</li><li>SAP experience will be useful in daily work</li><li>Singaporeans only</li><li>Any other duties as and when assigned</li></ul><p><br /></p>",
